title: Dez Bryant | Mental Health, NFT's and Empowering Athletes - Part 2
description:
I AM ATHLETE Miami Season 3: Episode 5

Dallas Cowboys legend, Dez Bryant joins Brandon Marshall, Chad Johnson, Fred Taylor and Channing Crowder in episode 5 of I AM ATHLETE Miami. Dez peels back the curtains on his struggles with anxiety and depression. Dez and his business partner Dan go on to educate the cast on how NFT's work and how they plan to use it to give the power back to the athletes.
